quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"Min njippini ii mbo e jehma leylatul qadiri."
  97,2,"Holko anndinat ma leylatul qadiri."
  97,3,"Leylatu qadri oon …ďuri ujunere lewru mo∆ī∆īude."
  97,4,"Maleykaaji na telloo wond'ude e jibriil e sakkitoore joom mu'en e kala yamiroore."
  97,5,"Kombo kisal tan ha fajiri feera."
  98,1,"Wonaana …ďeen he'efer…ďe joom defte en ko seertu…ďe ha ari e ma…ď…ďe dallillaaji pee√Ī…ói."
  98,2,"Ko o nelaa…óo ummaade e Alla dursittoo…óo …óereeji la…ď…ďinaa…ói."
  98,3,"Hina heen defte po'occii…óe."
  98,4,"Seertaani …ďeen tottaa…ďe defte si wona caggal nde ari e mu'en ko …ďanngi."
  98,5,"…ďe njamiraako si wona yoo…ďe ndew Alla tawa he…ďe la…ď…ďinani mbo diine pooccii…óo …ďe ndarana juulde …ďe tottira askal ko …óuum woni diine po'occii…óo."
  98,6,"Pellet …ďeen he'efer…ďe ummaade e joom defte en e sirku…ďe hina e jayngol jahatnama …ďe caasa toon ha pooma ko …ďeen ngoni …ďur…ďe bon'de e tagoore he."
  98,7,"Pellet …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude ko …ďeen ngoni …ďurbe mo∆ī∆īude e winndere he."